SELECT
  NOW() as time,
  COALESCE(D."DeviceName", 'nil') as "DeviceName",
  count(distinct(D."DeviceId")) as "Count"
FROM
  "DeviceInfo" D JOIN "CityInfo" C ON D."id" = C."DeviceInfoId" AND $__timeFilter(C."RequestTime")

GROUP BY 
  D."DeviceName"
ORDER BY "Count" desc

SELECT NOW() as time, "DeviceName", sum("count") as "count" FROM (
    SELECT "DeviceName", "count" FROM total_devices
    UNION
    SELECT 
        COALESCE("DeviceName", 'nil') as "DeviceName",
        count(distinct(D."DeviceId")) as "count"
    FROM
        "DeviceInfo" D JOIN "CityInfo" C ON D."id" = C."DeviceInfoId"
    WHERE D."FirstRequestTime" > (SELECT refresh_time FROM view_state WHERE view_name = 'total_devices')
    GROUP BY 
        "DeviceName"
) td
GROUP BY "DeviceName"
ORDER BY "count" desc;

select
  COALESCE("FaceVersion", 'nil') as "Version",
  count(distinct("DeviceInfoId")) as "Count"
from "CityInfo" 

WHERE
  $__timeFilter("RequestTime")
group by "FaceVersion"
order by "Count" desc

SELECT "Version", sum("Count") as "Count" FROM (
    SELECT "Version", "Count" FROM total_versions
    UNION
    select
        "FaceVersion" as "Version",
        count(distinct("DeviceInfoId")) as "Count"
    from "CityInfo" C
    WHERE C."RequestTime" > (SELECT refresh_time FROM view_state WHERE view_name = 'total_versions')
    group by "FaceVersion"
) tv
GROUP BY "Version"
ORDER BY "Count" desc;

SELECT
  count(distinct("DeviceInfoId")) AS metric,
  max("Lat") AS lat, max("Lon") lon, "CityName"

FROM "CityInfo"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("RequestTime") AND "CityName" is not NULL
GROUP BY "CityName"

SELECT
  "CityName",
  count(distinct("DeviceInfoId")) AS "Count"

FROM "CityInfo"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("RequestTime") AND "Lat" IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY "CityName"
ORDER BY "Count"
